Author: Alright#0419
Content: Ok, kind of nailed down exactly what my problem was

Author: Alright#0419
Content: KMD daemon was showing a tiny amount more in `getbalance` than the UTXOs actually added up to

Author: Alright#0419
Content: so it was convinced it had more unspent UTXOs than it actually did, if it tried to use these UTXOs, the notarization round would fail

Author: Alright#0419
Content: fix was empty the wallet entirely, resend coins back to wallet and resplit UTXOs
